      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "公子甲、公子乙、公子丙、公子丁同上。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00002",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "公子甲"
      ],
      "text": "春游芳草地，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00003",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "公子乙"
      ],
      "text": "夏赏荷花池。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00004",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丙"
      ],
      "text": "秋饮菊花酒，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00005",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "冬吟白雪诗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00006",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子甲"
      ],
      "text": "列位请了！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00007",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子乙",
        "公子丙",
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "请了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00008",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子甲"
      ],
      "text": "今有王相府，高搭彩楼，抛球招婿。你我前去接彩。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00009",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子乙",
        "公子丙",
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "请！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00010",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "公子甲、公子乙、公子丙、公子丁同走圆场。门官暗上。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00011",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "你们都是接彩的吗？往里边儿请吧！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00012",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "公子甲、公子乙、公子丙同下。门官拦公子丁。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00013",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "咳，咳！你这老头儿，是干什么的？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00014",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "我也是接彩的。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00015",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "你年纪这么大啦，不能进去。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00016",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "我是人老心不老。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00017",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "不行，不能进去。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00018",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "我跟你商量商量：没有胡子，能进去吗？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00019",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "等你没有胡子的时候，再商量吧！去，去！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00020",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "公子丁转身摘胡子。月老持云帚引薛平贵同暗上，同进门，同下。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00021",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "现在胡子没了，能进去了吧？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00022",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "还是不能进去。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00023",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "为什么哪？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00024",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "到底你是年纪大了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00025",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "我这个人有个脾气：你不让我进去，我偏要进去。你叫我进去，我倒不进去了！",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00026",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "啊！那么我来试验试验。老头儿，我不让你进去！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00027",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "我偏要进去。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00028",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "我让你进去了！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00029",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "那我就进去吧。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00030",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "公子丁下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00031",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "好！我上了他当了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00032",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "门官下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00033",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "梳妆打扮出绣房，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00034",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四丫鬟引王宝钏同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00035",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "后堂内辞别了二老爹娘。老天爷若称了奴的愿望，早与那平贵配成双。叫丫鬟带路彩楼上，",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00036",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四丫鬟引王宝钏同上楼，四丫鬟分站两旁。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00037",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "手扶着栏杆——",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00038",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "看端详：也有王孙公子样，也有客旅与经商。举目抬头——",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00039",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "四下望，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00040",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王宝钏望。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00041",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "因何不见那花郎？花园赠金对他讲，看来他是无义郎！不打彩球回府往，",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00042",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "公子甲、公子乙、公子丙、公子丁同暗上，月老引薛平贵同上。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00043",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "公子甲",
        "公子乙",
        "公子丙",
        "公子丁"
      ],
      "text": "别回去！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00044",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "回府去怎对二爹娘？姻缘本是月老掌，哪有个自己做主张！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00045",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "看彩球！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00046",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "彩球撇下任人抢，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00047",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王宝钏抛彩球。公子甲、公子乙、公子丙、公子丁同抢。薛平贵得球。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00048",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "月老"
      ],
      "text": "彩球打中讨饭郎。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00049",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "公子甲、公子乙、公子丙、公子丁、薛平贵、月老自两边分下。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00050",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "耳边厢又听得人喧嚷：彩球打中讨饭的郎。想必就是薛平贵？不由奴家意彷徨。丫鬟带路——",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00051",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "回府往，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00052",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四丫鬟扶王宝钏同下楼。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00053",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "回府去禀告二老爹娘。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021002_e00054",
      "play_id": "03021002",
      "scene_id": "03021002_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四丫鬟随王宝钏同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    }
